{"tid":1046006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貼文求相一日近9萬人響應　「我們愛妳」　患癌愛狗女孩綻笑容","createTime":"2019-03-04T02:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T02:52:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a26b584193a31b7e28c1593a3ce985eb6f8bc6","tid":1046006,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495477/org/00fb5897bb0c94e9f91a31ac101e118e.jpg/GUGzNQEvfvHnudJNhXSKy6IiRBedvdtcvnPdYL5z3WA?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495477%2Forg%2F00fb5897bb0c94e9f91a31ac101e118e.jpg%2FGUGzNQEvfvHnudJNhXSKy6IiRBedvdtcvnPdYL5z3WA%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=e6eec5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國威斯康星州7歲女孩梅爾滕斯（Emma Mertens）不幸被診斷出患有腦瘤，由於她非常喜歡動物，於是其家人向動物收容所徵求狗狗相片，為她打氣。收容所在Facebook發文後，短短一日內已有來自世界各地的8.7萬人響應，分享「毛孩」照片。<br />\n<br />\n動物保護團體「威斯康星人道協會」（Wisconsin Humane Society）上月28日在Facebook發文稱，7歲女孩梅爾滕斯被診斷出患有腦瘤，而且無法動手術移除，因為她很喜歡動物，家人希望收集多些狗狗的照片，讓她在接受治療時好過一點。<br />\n<br />\n網友立即紛紛貼出寵物照片，除了狗，還有貓、馬、狼等各種動物。有一隻叫布拉德利（Bradley）的狗同樣不幸患有腫瘤，鼻子脫毛，留言「但是朋友和愛會給你力量，我們愛你！」還有一隻叫安格斯牛肉（Angus Beef）的，其留言是「你好，我今年也因為腦裏有腫瘤而病了，但我今天感覺不錯，希望你能和我做朋友！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495462/org/f3ce6621368d4ad2f9384019bf41ec41.JPG/BemipZ58RDMH1JC0BMhN9ePH6Re0DbF_f7V3G3-1dxs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495462%2Forg%2Ff3ce6621368d4ad2f9384019bf41ec41.JPG%2FBemipZ58RDMH1JC0BMhN9ePH6Re0DbF_f7V3G3-1dxs&h=664ad17b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495467/org/e608745317bb0388c6d507fd41a82ea7.JPG/2Q6zpY1oRkOaKq4KDuJVFmjPsfAl2LvAKhGKECoRihA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495467%2Forg%2Fe608745317bb0388c6d507fd41a82ea7.JPG%2F2Q6zpY1oRkOaKq4KDuJVFmjPsfAl2LvAKhGKECoRihA&h=b4b18f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495465/org/5f04e8f2f621bbe67ab9a5f1e35e741f.JPG/MqJUH7dDEfJ6JArF14xqlhQMtFRvILukzYXUxc2F1MU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495465%2Forg%2F5f04e8f2f621bbe67ab9a5f1e35e741f.JPG%2FMqJUH7dDEfJ6JArF14xqlhQMtFRvILukzYXUxc2F1MU&h=0425ed22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495468/org/3d1659a247588a94a6074154e8caefbc.JPG/HqKQrVAxyxgQlPwtw_vVAl_Y0cHmw2r0E2fquhNn6ro\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495468%2Forg%2F3d1659a247588a94a6074154e8caefbc.JPG%2FHqKQrVAxyxgQlPwtw_vVAl_Y0cHmw2r0E2fquhNn6ro&h=9fe9fc50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495466/org/49216eb22e1a24201ed86c466aeedd54.JPG/LKVVeI9ZAt8tq6uHyxcuZabeyern1IlJ2Msk-djLJPk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495466%2Forg%2F49216eb22e1a24201ed86c466aeedd54.JPG%2FLKVVeI9ZAt8tq6uHyxcuZabeyern1IlJ2Msk-djLJPk&h=c7651121&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2495469/org/9476cf6418180d0fa7e68a85cffb7d32.JPG/3Wuib-vw_V6lCejNv6X7DUv2wOWsiCdcZXYXHWV2Fx0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2495469%2Forg%2F9476cf6418180d0fa7e68a85cffb7d32.JPG%2F3Wuib-vw_V6lCejNv6X7DUv2wOWsiCdcZXYXHWV2Fx0&h=9696b6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「威斯康星人道協會」發文一日就接獲近8.8萬則留言、逾萬人分享，雖然網友與梅爾滕斯素未謀面，但都真摯地為她加油打氣，希望那些可愛動物照片能助她度過難關。<br />\n<br />\n除了Facebook留言，梅爾滕斯一家還收到2500封電郵，郵箱也塞滿了打氣信。小女孩的爸爸說：「小狗照片令她綻放笑容，感謝所有鼓勵她的人，你們的善舉令我們很感動。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/300839/%E8%B2%BC%E6%96%87%E6%B1%82%E7%9B%B8%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E8%BF%919%E8%90%AC%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%A9%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%84%9B%E5%A6%B3-%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E6%84%9B%E7%8B%97%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E7%B6%BB%E7%AC%91%E5%AE%B9#media_id=2495469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.